title: Week 8 WYMT Team of the Week: Shelby Valley
text:
Week 8 WYMT Team of the Week: Shelby Valley Updated: Tue 10:27 PM, Oct 20, 2015 / Headlines List / Article 
PIKEVILLE, Ky. (WYMT) -- The Shelby Valley Wildcats are the WYMT Team of the Week for week eight of the high school football season. 
The 'Cats defeated undefeated Leslie County to win the class 2A, District 8 title. 
Jordan Hampton, Chandler Rowe and Kasey Tackett all rushed for over 100 yards individually in the game. 
Valley finishes out the regular season with home games against Allen Central and Paintsville.
